Limitations There are some limitations to this study. Each person has an individual perspective, framework, and worldview through which to make sense of such policies. The findings of this specific analysis are limited to this author’s perspectives and worldview. The supportive literature is also limited to the perspective of its authors. Finally, this study could not address the plethora o f literature that exists since the implementation of mandatory minimums, and there may be gaps in the literature due to this.
